room_title: Escape room "The Laboratory" by Amazing Escape Room Cherry Hill in Collingswood
room_address: 2050 Springdale Rd Suite 200 Cherry Hill, NJ 08003
room_description: Help! Someone has poisoned the Swedish Prime Minister and they only have an hour to live. There is hope though for the Prime Minister. Hidden in the Lab are all the necessary steps to make an antidote to save the Prime Minister. If you can solve the clues, puzzled and tricks and find that antidote in under an hour, you will be the envy of a nation. However, if you don’t make it out of the lab in time, you’d better get a shovel and a passport.
